Speaking of your work with Xbox Kinect sensors, what are your complaints about modern cameras?
Missing resolution, depth or something?
- Basically, this generation is what we can build on in our work on 3D recognition.
Of course, it would be nice to get 8 megapixels at 1,000 kph.
