We tried to make a program that would appeal to all generations, including children.
For example, in Prague, Chinaski, Support Lesbiens, Illustratosphere with Dan Bart, The Tap Tap, Marjan Bango and Irzy Suki will perform.
You can find out more on www.kpks.cz.
